    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value. It's a practical and sturdy companion for your daily needs!",
