    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require a dedicated owner ready for a project. The engine is running roughly and likely requires a full diagnostic and potential overhaul, while the transmission shifts are noticeably harsh. Externally, the car shows its age with significant rust patches, faded paint, and several dents. The interior has sustained heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is priced to reflect these extensive needs and is sold strictly as-is.",
