    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a practical choice for a driver looking for a functional car at a lower price point. While it remains reliable for daily commutes, there are visible signs of wear including some exterior scratches and interior upholstery aging. The engine runs consistently, though it may benefit from a tune-up in the near future to ensure continued performance.",
